<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_cf344133-9e56-4ab9-9b85-18d84e7a6bd2" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><sptc>B5D3</sptc><title id="_64e89086-5c6f-4ae6-a646-1398a686f307">Non-Drinking Water Service</title><subclause id="_0795f449-7d4a-4652-a7b3-32c48679f78f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_3334e519-7fa4-401b-bdaf-24ef9afc2416">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_579efd80-484d-4feb-8768-3200d8d36ddf" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service or supply may have a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1233_1.0.0.xml#_b3f409ec-8f72-48d9-8a64-0dc9d5fb5d67" id="_0aeb971a-1af5-40f3-8202-d72422093eca" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">cross-connection</xref> to another separate <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_63fa0980-102f-4e44-a14a-03c1bc30cf65" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service on the same site provided it is protected with a low hazard device. The low hazard device must be selected and installed in accordance with Section 4 of AS/NZS 3500.1</p></subclause><subclause id="_c60252fd-849c-45e5-9968-eb818224dd35" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_fc53a68c-ad5d-4a4e-898d-12f4feadfcf9">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Where a site is served by a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_f27dfb5d-737b-4891-91d6-48d8f0e12e1d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator’s</xref> drinking water supply, appropriate <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_13182e48-d692-4d06-86f5-8b1e64906838" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment protection</xref> must be: </p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_9c74ea13-4977-4dc9-aef8-783d2d16584d">selected and installed with the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_d97b2dfc-6d61-4219-8c65-5f8f5e0c7574" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref> relevant regulations, guidelines, policies or similar documents; or</li><li id="_b6711ee8-31f8-4daa-81ef-d2bee6018575">where the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_657af90e-5d23-4c63-b4ff-c376881973c4" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref> does not prescribe requirements for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_eef04ff4-2017-47d4-8e9f-e0b3dc0c0417" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment protection</xref>, assign a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_99c179ff-e2f9-473d-9aa6-345064f4a7d7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment protection</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_cad807ba-7cab-4e7c-8019-ca94605957ed" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Rating</xref> in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9560_0.38.0.xml#_49ef982c-45dc-4a90-9596-f2b6fa0712a5" id="_c22c7919-3985-4e01-9a33-2cf7a699f12b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">B5D7(10)</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9560_0.38.0.xml#_637c1753-6579-4f76-ab3e-826e43429458" id="_61b2c167-c613-4a59-8d1a-90cdcf616392" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">B5D7(11)</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9560_0.38.0.xml#_1c32bfcf-d609-42b0-981b-f4ea31656712" id="_df6528ce-95f4-4336-8259-1b78b47bd2b7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">B5D7(12)</xref>, and select and install appropriate <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_e4bbb0bf-6f2d-438f-be15-1426dd06be0a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment protection</xref> in accordance with Section 4 of AS/NZS 3500.1</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_536b34f6-7e21-4d43-991e-eec4ac852cfa"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Where a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_2b2b368b-6b45-4898-a1a5-f04edfb2fc80" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Containment Protection</xref> backflow prevention device is installed external of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_0e378e31-1dce-4771-94f5-7a07bb2a14b4" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref> water meter, the valve remains the responsibility of the property owner unless owned by the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_a5944cb5-78fd-4b48-a4ad-3b4e6bfca7a9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref>, including any testing, servicing and maintenance that may be required.</p><p>Where the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_92ca620c-380e-47b9-b5c8-2937c5ae82b9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref> prescribes <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_4453b430-febc-429b-b800-27adc63fd218" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment protection</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_9ff82dee-9477-4788-8bde-17fe744e72cc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hazard ratings</xref> above the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_91c053ed-36b7-471b-bb31-d08c3714472a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hazard rating</xref> set out in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9560_0.38.0.xml#_49ef982c-45dc-4a90-9596-f2b6fa0712a5" id="_c52a4f6c-1fb8-478d-8b36-16d5777b8901" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">B5D7(10)</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9560_0.38.0.xml#_637c1753-6579-4f76-ab3e-826e43429458" id="_f5e4e860-ef34-43db-844d-fd8799d7d95b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">B5D7(11)</xref>, and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9560_0.38.0.xml#_1c32bfcf-d609-42b0-981b-f4ea31656712" id="_9cd0f702-1a8c-4086-bf73-8c82882f6c56" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">B5D7(12)</xref>, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_aeaf52b6-72ca-4e33-905d-63467e9b091a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref> is responsible for the regulation of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1228_0.6.0.xml#_a7483c3c-cd8a-4c37-8f2b-8e4fba0e0989" id="_189f6592-eb35-474c-bbec-1682e556e6d8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment</xref> backflow installation.</p></callout><callout id="_d86de1b0-af4d-4f9f-bf3b-b125c01b040c"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption"/><p>B5D3 is not applicable to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_db0be775-54e2-429b-8a6a-22686320260b" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service used for agricultural purposes where the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_d6704f31-6c5f-41c5-8983-3e280ffe1004" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service is supplied solely by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_ab7a2358-1ffd-4398-ac80-f87279444360" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service(s)and is fully independent from any other water service.</p></callout><callout id="_53fe4d7c-0d71-47a5-89a0-e99ca923ee75"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>For the purposes of B5D3, a ‘separate’ <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_35ced56f-e2e3-448d-a280-4d351b1bb357" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service exists where multiple <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_c19c4f22-b08b-48fb-bac3-e70a922a9c5a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> services are on the same site and each is supplied by water from different sources.</p><p>For example, on a site connected to both recycled water and bore water, both may be considered <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_464518f6-bd58-4f4a-9044-bf01147a9cf1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> services and are supplied by different sources. Therefore, each is a ‘separate’ <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1378_4.3.0.xml#_cfc4fec0-3cb7-41d6-b176-4a92d4cdb221" id="_fc77dbed-1a75-4f9a-a979-b9afe363f503" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-drinking water</xref> service.</p></callout></clause>